title: (Thurs Early Bird) Jordan Davis In-Studio to Talk About His CMA Nominations, Wife and Tour + We Play Elder vs. Millennial + Morgan Gives Us Her Millennial Movie Review
itunes:title: (Thurs Early Bird) Jordan Davis In-Studio to Talk About His CMA Nominations, Wife and Tour + We Play Elder vs. Millennial + Morgan Gives Us Her Millennial Movie Review
description:
Jordan Davis joins us in-studio to talk about his CMA Nominations, his wife, his favorite things about touring and more! We play Elder vs. Millennial and the punishment for the loser is the worst yet. Plus, Morgan gives us a new Millennial Movie Review of the movie "Stand By Me." 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
